1. *Sretna* je što je našla posao. (She is happy that she found a job.)
2. *Sretni* su ljudi koji su to činili. (The people who did it are happy.)
3. *Sretnom* su se sreća okrenula. (Happiness has turned to her.)
4. *Sretno* se išlo na put. (They went on a journey happily.)
5. *Sretnim* smo se rastali. (We said goodbye happily.)